children.name: “Hey” has great features for both students & companies.
children.content:
“Hey” has great features
for both students & companies.

children.name: On hey you can connect to your fellow students and share what is happening in your college/university through a post with a picture or video and also receive updates from your interested Universities by following.
children.content: On hey you can connect to your fellow students and share what is happening in your college/university through a post with a picture or video and also receive updates from your interested Universities by following.

children.name: Students can build their resumes in a simple way and also able to explore the Internships, Part time and full time job opportunities. Students can follow their interested companies to receive personal notification on career opportunities.
children.content: Students can build their resumes in a simple way and also able to explore the Internships, Part time and full time job opportunities. Students can follow their interested companies to receive personal notification on career opportunities.

children.name: Based on common Interests, hey will connect the students beyond your class, college, city and country. You can share your thoughts, ideas to the world and enrich your knowledge in a fun way.
children.content: Based on common Interests, hey will connect the students beyond your class, college, city and country.  You can share your thoughts, ideas to the world and enrich your knowledge in a fun way.

children.name: A one stop shop to see ads related to job fares, learning events, better online learning courses across globe and commercial ads related to fashion, food etc.
children.content: A one stop shop to see ads related to job fares, learning events, better online learning courses across globe and commercial ads related to fashion, food etc.

children.name: Companies are welcome to buy ad space to present their opportunities and find the correct target audience(students) which they fail to get from social media apps.
children.content: Companies are welcome to buy ad space to present their opportunities and find the correct target audience(students) which they fail to get from social media apps.

children.name: Hey is a single mobile platform designed only for college/University students to bring students college life into their hands. Hey helps to share what is happening inside their college/university and also get the updates from their interested universities. Hey also helps to shape out student careers by exploring Intern & fresh graduate jobs and also assist in building CV etc. Ad’s sections helps students to explore events, jobs fare, university admissions and course offers across globe.
children.content:
Hey is a single mobile platform designed only for college/University students to bring students college life into their hands.  Hey helps to share what is happening inside their college/university and also get the updates from their interested universities.

Hey also helps to shape out student careers by exploring Intern & fresh graduate jobs and also assist in building CV etc.  Ad’s sections helps students to explore events, jobs fare, university admissions and course offers across globe.
